[the second version]

v4w.enko - "3D G_RD=N sc_02" - is one more scene of a garden of  forms created in 3d capable with  augmented reality. Minted to the 3d NFT and possible rotate, zoom, pan. We can suit our room with "parametric" garden to change the perception of outside world with Augmented Reality function. 

Technically 3 components (algorithms) are used: 
- array of smooth lofts through random points 
- "3d voronoi" diagram through random points population
- exploded 3d mesh variation.
